\newlabel{fig:tail_power}{{3}{8}{Detection power for tail effects (upper 5\% of distribution shifted by X$\sigma $). \tacet achieves 100\% detection at 20$\sigma $ tail shifts, demonstrating the W$_1$ distance's sensitivity to rare outliers}{figure.caption.30}{}}
